mil.emp3.api

Class Ellipse

  • java.lang.Object
    • mil.emp3.api.abstracts.Container
      • mil.emp3.api.abstracts.Feature<IGeoEllipse>
        • mil.emp3.api.Ellipse
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IContainer, IFeature<IGeoEllipse>, IGeoAltitudeMode, IGeoBase, IGeoContainer, IGeoEllipse, IGeoPositionGroup, IGeoRenderable

    public class Ellipse
extends Feature<IGeoEllipse>
implements IGeoEllipse
    This class implements an ellipse feature. It requires a single coordinate that indicates the geographic position of the center of the ellipse.
